snippet.textDisplay: Apne walden se aulad kisi cheez ki bhi farmaish karna kufr he kyon woh khud Allah pak se mangte he. Har chhote bachche ko agar ye sikhaya jay ke nabi se mohabbat ya nabi ke wasile ya nabi ke sadqe mangna ghalat he to butt parsaton ki jamat me vapasi bahut khareeb hojayegi. Jo kufr ke fatwa dete hain woh nabi ka ahteram dil se nahi karte jo nabi ko Allah ne bhi apna zaria banaya Quran Jahilon tak pahuncha kar musalman banaya. Allah Aur Uske Farishtey salaam aur darud bhejte hain nabi par aye imaan waalon tum bhi kasrat se salaam wa darud bhejo apne nabi par.Aur Jo Salam wa darud ka matlab bhi nahi samajhte Allah unke Dil wa dimaagh ko Duniawi chamak mehfooz farma.
